{{afc comment|Wikidata entry [[Category:Has wikidata]][[d:Q85882196]] Wikidata name: [[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 09:48, 11 June 2025 (UTC)}} '''Taki-no-o Shrine''' (瀧尾神社, 滝尾神社) refers to Shinto shrines across Japan. As of now, there are 13 shrines registered under the old-style kanji 瀧尾神社, 4 under the new-style kanji 滝尾神社, and 1 shrine incorporating the name 瀧尾神社 in its title.
